---
title: Cashew Chicken Stir-Fry with Broccoli over Jasmine Rice
description: When a cashew chicken craving strikes, you know how it is—you’ve gotta have it immediately, and nothing else will do. Fortunately, this dish is super speedy to whip up in your own kitchen. In just 25 minutes, you can have steamy rice, tender chicken and broccoli, tangy-sweet sauce, and crunchy cashews. Comfort food at its finest? We think so.
